Package: rtemis.llm
Title: LLMs and Agentic AI
Version: 0.7.2
Date: 2026-04-22
Authors@R: person(given = "E.D.", family = "Gennatas", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), 
    email = "gennatas@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9280-3609"))
Description: Provides functionality to interface with Large Language Models. Supports reasoning, 
    structured output, memory management, and secure tool use. Allows creation of custom LLM-based 
    workflows and agentic AI systems using a functional user-facing frontend and an S7 backend. 
    Includes map() llmapply() for efficient batch inference. Supports 'Ollama', 'OpenAI'-compatible, 
    and 'Anthropic'-compatible endpoints.
